com.att.aro.main

Class DetailedResultRowPanel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.att.aro.main.DetailedResultRowPanel

  • public class DetailedResultRowPanel
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a row in the Best Practices tab. Each row represents one Best Practices test which has a category ( Caching, Connections, or Other), an icon, a test name, an About line, and Results details.
